{"tid":375483,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人用呢種方法洗車","createTime":"2017-08-26T13:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T17:38:07.000Z","uid":80308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e76d4641cbbb3dc4d1c268ed2a9b87d7b6189aa0","tid":375483,"uid":80308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T13:52:11.000Z","msg":"一直都想買部洗車器,但有個問題<br />\n1. 如果插點煙器,或者內置有得充電嗰D,多數都唔夠力/水壓,沖唔走晒D污跡<br />\n2. 要夠力既,一定要插濕電<br />\n<br />\n但喺香港,屋企停車場就算俾你洗車,都無插頭可用,<br />\n出去搵個空曠既地方,又係無插頭<br />\n<br />\n所以一直想搵個portable既三腳插充電器<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺indiegogo見到呢部充電器,有三腳插,又有成54000mAh,<br />\n好似好吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/plug-the-world-s-most-powerful-battery-pack-powerbank-solar--2#/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiegogo.com%2Fprojects%2Fplug-the-world-s-most-powerful-battery-pack-powerbank-solar--2%23%2F&d=rFYKuXzkG0mmulhzOWl5Ap4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a0cf4f9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/plug-the-world-s-most-powerful-battery-pack-powerbank-solar--2#/</a><br />\n<br />\n有無人用呢類充電器駁洗車器黎洗車?<br />\n<br />\n不過喺amazon見到,呢款野好似寄唔到黎HK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5023d81fb7e1cabf509f1562a42dc0b43b9821f","tid":375483,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:01:13.000Z","msg":"有水有電有高壓泡槍真係好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917e5b4c50f086cb1201976662a15f548508f46a","tid":375483,"uid":80308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有水有電有高壓泡槍真係好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家爭電, 呢部充電機行得通既話就搞掂"},{"pid":"68a6da89d7d5cdcfac1afb6106c81c9cf575c66f","tid":375483,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:07:05.000Z","msg